Network contains three catogeries of components:
  1) End to End devices -- smartphone,tablet,printer,camera etc etc.
  2) intermediate devices -- wireless router, wired router, firewall, multilayer switch etc etc.
  3) Network media -- LAN( large area network) , WAN( wired area network) , Wireless network.
ISP( internet service provider) --- which provides internet to network of devices connected to it.
